libplctag
------------------------------------------
This library for Linux and Windows (not heavily tested) provides a means of
accessing PLCs to read and write simple data.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.6-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libplctag-devel-2.6.14-1bl1
  libplctag2.6-2.6.14-1bl1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.45.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.6-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/libplctag/libplctag

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/libplctag/libplctag/archive/refs/tags/v2.6.14.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libplctag-2.6.14-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libplctag-2.6.14-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libplctag-2.6.14-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libplctag-2.6.14-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libplctag2.6-2.6.14-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libplctag-devel-2.6.14-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libplctag)
  /usr/bin/modbus_server.exe
  /usr/bin/tag_rw2.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libplctag.README
  /usr/share/doc/libplctag/LICENSE-1.MPL
  /usr/share/doc/libplctag/LICENSE-2.LGPL
  /usr/share/doc/libplctag/README.md

(libplctag2.6)
  /usr/bin/cygplctag-2.6.dll

(libplctag-devel)
  /usr/include/libplctag.h
  /usr/lib/libplctag.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libplctag.pc

------------------

